high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the counter, turn left again and walk up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and take the apple out of the microwave then close the microwave.
Turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the apple inside on a shelf, then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the now chilled apple, then close the door.
Walk over to the blue bin to the left of the fridge.
Put the chilled apple into the blue bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in a blue bin.

high_descs: Cross the kitchen and go to face the red microwave.
Open the microwave and grab the apple that's in there.
Bring the apple over to the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and let it get cool, then take it out again.
Bring the apple with you a step to the left and look at the blue trash can.
Put the apple in the trash can.
Walk ahead to the counter, then turn left and face the microwave.
Take the apple out of the microwave.
Place the apple in the fridge to the left of the lettuce on the bottom shelf.
Place the apple in the bin in front of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple in a garbage bin.
